item.title: CVE-2015-10015|2024-08-06T08:58:24.666Z -- glidernet -- ogn-live
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as critical, has been found in glidernet ogn-live. This issue affects some unknown processing. The manipulation leads to sql injection. The patch is named bc0f19965f760587645583b7624d66a260946e01. It is recommended to apply a patch to fix this issue. The associated identifier of this vulnerability is VDB-217487.
